snippet.title: Siska Leontyne 【NIJISANJI / にじさんじ】
snippet.description:
Hello I'm Siska Leontyne, call me Siska for short
I'm an Elite security officer and Vtuber from NIJISANJI /  にじさんじ from Indonesia
I usually stream some games and do whatever weird things 
Game that I usualy play are FPS/TPS, Horror, MOBA and RPG! 

I hope we can get along~ (￣▽￣)/ ☆
